    The Newzbin column will map listed Newzbin categories to your own.<br/>
    <!--#if not $have_cats#-->
        <br/>Click <a href="javascript:lr('config/categories/catinit_newzbin')"><b>HERE</b></a> to setup newzbin categories.<br/><br/>
    <!--#end if#-->
